WEBVTT

01:39.400 --> 01:43.520
[Road to Success]

01:44.490 --> 01:47.880
[Episode 11]

02:21.770 --> 02:22.530
Where is he?

02:37.150 --> 02:38.070
It's him.

02:38.310 --> 02:39.440
He was following me.

02:40.870 --> 02:42.910
I wasn't following her.

02:42.910 --> 02:44.240
I was trying to find you.

02:51.150 --> 02:52.560
He's my manager.

02:58.280 --> 02:59.590
You have a manager?

03:00.870 --> 03:01.470
There's nothing weird about

03:01.470 --> 03:03.730
Nanton's coach having a manager, right?

03:07.680 --> 03:08.520
What's wrong?

03:08.520 --> 03:09.910
What's with your outfit?

03:09.910 --> 03:11.280
Can't afford to buy a pair of pants?

03:11.280 --> 03:12.970
You know nothing about fashion.

03:12.970 --> 03:13.810
See this?

03:15.240 --> 03:17.520
This is the "missing lower body" look.

03:18.079 --> 03:19.810
It's really in style right now.

03:20.190 --> 03:21.630
If you don't button up your coat now,

03:21.630 --> 03:24.690
I'm seriously going to make
your lower half disappear.

03:25.079 --> 03:25.940
So out of touch.

03:27.590 --> 03:28.310
Ms. Lin.

03:30.470 --> 03:32.070
I've heard so much about you.

03:32.630 --> 03:34.590
Let me formally introduce myself.

03:35.240 --> 03:36.120
I am Felix Yu,

03:37.120 --> 03:37.970
Winfred's manager.

03:37.970 --> 03:39.750
[Felix Yu, Manager of Yongchuan Hengjiu
Youth Football Club]

03:45.470 --> 03:46.320
Too bad.

03:46.470 --> 03:48.430
I honestly thought
you were an exhibitionist,

03:48.430 --> 03:51.230
and I wanted to test
how strong your mentality was.

03:52.470 --> 03:53.120
You guys carry on.

03:53.120 --> 03:54.320
I'll leave you alone.

03:55.310 --> 03:56.550
I get your fashion.

04:02.840 --> 04:04.270
Seeing is believing.

04:04.470 --> 04:06.400
She really is an interesting girl.

04:06.680 --> 04:08.110
Did you come here just to mooch off mine?

04:08.110 --> 04:10.240
Let me tell you, they wouldn't fit.
They're too long for you.

04:10.240 --> 04:11.960
This is called fashion taste.

04:11.960 --> 04:13.190
Fashion taste.

04:13.190 --> 04:14.470
What do you know?

04:14.470 --> 04:15.360
Seriously.

04:19.560 --> 04:20.430
"Fashion."

04:23.160 --> 04:25.020
So, still two teaspoons of sugar?

04:26.270 --> 04:27.600
Giving me coffee at this hour?

04:27.600 --> 04:29.390
Are you trying to keep me up
and torture me all night?

04:29.390 --> 04:30.360
I'll have water.

04:32.800 --> 04:33.680
Alright then.

04:36.240 --> 04:39.360
Water, water, water. Okay.

04:44.240 --> 04:45.300
Here's your water.

04:48.560 --> 04:49.720
So,

04:50.680 --> 04:52.270
you're certain

04:53.000 --> 04:54.260
that she's not Spade Q?

04:58.240 --> 04:58.950
She's not.

05:01.190 --> 05:03.390
Bro, I remember you were a materialist.

05:03.630 --> 05:05.430
When did you become an idealist?

05:08.510 --> 05:10.040
Do you really think someone

05:10.240 --> 05:12.800
who's cute, a bit scatterbrained,
emotional,

05:12.800 --> 05:14.260
and considerate of others

05:14.800 --> 05:16.070
could be the kind of ruthless person

05:16.070 --> 05:18.730
who sets up traps to lead people
to their deaths?

05:22.160 --> 05:23.560
Would you put training wheels on a bike

05:23.560 --> 05:25.750
and force yourself to ride it
just to win a bet?

05:23.760 --> 05:26.080
♪ Two souls aligned ♪

05:27.630 --> 05:29.510
♪ In silent gravity ♪

05:28.270 --> 05:30.170
Would you cheat on a bet

05:30.600 --> 05:32.600
by having your students help you
meet your exercise targets?

05:31.780 --> 05:33.909
♪ Heal my heart ♪

05:34.270 --> 05:36.020
Would you plot against your neighbor,

05:34.530 --> 05:37.200
♪ With every part of you ♪

05:36.120 --> 05:37.920
only to end up scaring yourself?

05:38.270 --> 05:39.700
Would you do something just for laughs,

05:39.700 --> 05:41.780
♪ Our words flow ♪

05:40.000 --> 05:42.860
then end up using your neighbor's
washing machine?

05:43.180 --> 05:45.409
♪ A gentle stream ♪

05:44.310 --> 05:45.120
Besides,

05:45.310 --> 05:46.560
she was willing to put her own life
on the line

05:46.560 --> 05:47.920
to save a student.

05:47.490 --> 05:49.670
♪ They glow like fireflies ♪

05:49.190 --> 05:50.560
Do you think Spade Q would ever do that?

05:50.330 --> 05:52.850
♪ Inside a silken dream ♪

05:52.040 --> 05:53.900
The last time you talked this much

05:54.630 --> 05:56.190
was when you were making a case for Jason.

05:55.060 --> 06:00.970
♪ We talk the cool night, breeze away ♪

05:58.920 --> 06:01.120
Anyway, when it comes to these details,

06:01.270 --> 06:03.510
I think they're more convincing
than any data could ever be.

06:02.890 --> 06:04.670
♪ We trace the roads ♪

06:04.510 --> 06:06.160
Okay, got it.

06:05.290 --> 06:08.400
♪ That never see an end ♪

06:07.120 --> 06:10.320
So in your mind,
the probability of her being Spade Q is...

06:11.080 --> 06:14.680
♪ We softly calm the hidden doubt ♪

06:11.630 --> 06:14.360
Never mind, don't tell me.
I'll check for myself.

06:15.040 --> 06:17.000
I'm still not used to you
talking so much all of a sudden.

06:15.280 --> 06:19.970
♪ Seen in each other's eyes ♪

06:20.990 --> 06:22.470
♪ Bring to life ♪

06:21.410 --> 06:24.080
[The probability of Lin Wanxing
being Spade Q: 0%]

06:22.720 --> 06:23.920
Okay.

06:31.360 --> 06:33.560
Since she's been cleared of suspicion,

06:35.310 --> 06:36.710
shouldn't you get going?

06:37.630 --> 06:38.159
Where to?

06:40.270 --> 06:41.800
Remember to check your phone later.

06:41.800 --> 06:43.680
I'll send you information of

06:43.680 --> 06:45.159
all the clubs that are interested in you,

06:45.159 --> 06:46.960
especially Hengjiu.

06:48.800 --> 06:49.870
I think I get what you mean

06:49.870 --> 06:52.240
by that "especially."

06:52.510 --> 06:54.560
Alright, I won't keep you in suspense.

06:54.560 --> 06:55.830
I'm here

06:55.830 --> 06:58.190
on a mission from my goddess.

06:58.480 --> 07:00.360
She's offering a very high budget

07:00.360 --> 07:01.680
and is determined to get you, Mr. Winfred,

07:01.680 --> 07:02.750
to be the club coach.

07:02.750 --> 07:04.750
I'm just here to lay the groundwork.

07:06.510 --> 07:07.740
So, mission failed.

07:08.510 --> 07:09.430
Seriously?

07:09.870 --> 07:11.360
You're really going to be this ruthless
to your own buddy?

07:11.360 --> 07:12.560
Give me my watch back.

07:13.360 --> 07:14.960
I don't have it at the moment.

07:16.680 --> 07:17.680
Besides,

07:17.680 --> 07:19.750
you know perfectly well
what kind of person

07:19.750 --> 07:21.190
your sister, my goddess, is.

07:21.190 --> 07:22.310
Just you wait.

07:22.630 --> 07:23.480
I...

07:23.500 --> 07:24.750
You think I'm afraid of her?

07:24.750 --> 07:25.680
But I am.

07:26.240 --> 07:26.800
If she has something to say,

07:26.800 --> 07:28.600
she can come and tell me herself.

07:28.600 --> 07:30.040
Why send a minion over?

07:30.330 --> 07:32.110
I'm just here to lay the groundwork.

07:32.110 --> 07:34.370
I never intended to sway you or anything.

07:38.680 --> 07:40.120
I wonder what that manager

07:40.120 --> 07:41.800
wants with Winfred.

07:44.270 --> 07:45.830
Maybe I should go and finalize

07:45.830 --> 07:48.030
the coaching contract with him as well.

08:00.070 --> 08:02.270
"The football team will train as usual.

08:02.920 --> 08:04.360
But the indoor theory classes
need to be arranged

08:04.360 --> 08:05.560
as soon as possible."

08:06.830 --> 08:09.730
He still wants to have
indoor theory classes?

08:10.310 --> 08:13.240
Doesn't sound like someone
who's planning to leave.

08:19.650 --> 08:21.720
[Felix Yu, Manager of Yongchuan Hengjiu
Youth Football Club]

08:25.830 --> 08:27.600
If he really leaves the football team,

08:27.600 --> 08:28.870
what will happen?

08:32.470 --> 08:35.000
Guess I'll cross that bridge
when I come to it.

08:46.720 --> 08:48.000
I think

08:49.360 --> 08:50.690
I'll give this to Lin Lu.

09:01.040 --> 09:04.190
[Administrative Building]

09:10.960 --> 09:11.820
Director Qian.

09:15.240 --> 09:16.120
Director Qian?

09:20.430 --> 09:22.630
Whenever I need him, he's never around.

09:41.510 --> 09:43.120
Dear Director Qian,

09:43.120 --> 09:44.480
with the exams approaching,

09:44.480 --> 09:46.480
the team is in urgent need of...

09:50.150 --> 09:51.960
Would that sound too formal?

10:05.380 --> 10:06.580
[If I can save a heart
on the verge of breaking,]

10:06.610 --> 10:07.720
[then I will not have lived this life
in vain.]

10:06.750 --> 10:08.630
So Qian also reads poems?

10:21.720 --> 10:22.440
Ms. Lin?

10:23.270 --> 10:24.130
Director Qian.

10:24.390 --> 10:25.080
Are you

10:25.750 --> 10:26.610
looking for me?

10:27.120 --> 10:27.790
Yes.

10:27.790 --> 10:28.790
The football team needs an empty classroom

10:28.790 --> 10:30.390
for tutoring sessions.

10:30.390 --> 10:31.550
Have you tried
the Academic Affairs Office?

10:31.550 --> 10:32.510
I have.

10:32.510 --> 10:34.840
They said there are
no empty classrooms available.

10:34.840 --> 10:35.790
So,

10:35.790 --> 10:38.850
could you please step in
and help us out, Director Qian?

10:39.390 --> 10:41.440
I'm afraid there's nothing I can do
about that.

10:41.440 --> 10:44.970
You have to understand,
classrooms are reserved ahead of time,

10:45.080 --> 10:47.480
and every room is already fully scheduled.

10:47.670 --> 10:49.030
I can't just disrupt

10:49.030 --> 10:50.510
other teachers' classes, right?

10:50.510 --> 10:52.150
Try to figure something else out.

10:52.150 --> 10:54.320
Where there's a will, there's a way.

10:55.270 --> 10:55.870
Good luck.

10:58.550 --> 11:00.480
That was a really quick rejection.

11:09.910 --> 11:12.390
"Handsome, kind-hearted,
gentle yet powerful,

11:12.390 --> 11:14.870
the all-mighty Aladdin Qian Lamp:

11:14.870 --> 11:17.080
Please grant us
a place for tutoring sessions.

11:17.080 --> 11:18.080
Sincerely praying,

11:18.080 --> 11:19.550
desperate Lin.

11:21.600 --> 11:23.360
Come on, ladies first.

11:23.360 --> 11:24.120
You go first.

11:25.030 --> 11:26.270
Where did you go?

11:26.270 --> 11:27.200
To buy drinks.

11:28.720 --> 11:29.670
Continue.

11:30.480 --> 11:31.360
What's this?

11:32.580 --> 11:33.750
What is this thing?

11:35.600 --> 11:36.800
Such ugly packaging.

11:37.050 --> 11:37.670
Hold on.

11:37.670 --> 11:38.670
Don't open it yet.

11:39.790 --> 11:42.320
Could this be a bomb Wen Chengye planted

11:42.320 --> 11:43.440
to get back at you?

11:43.910 --> 11:45.270
-What are you talking about?
-What a waste.

11:45.270 --> 11:47.000
It's not entirely impossible.

11:52.750 --> 11:53.910
Have you ever received

11:53.910 --> 11:55.670
anything weird like this before?

11:54.750 --> 11:56.490
[100 free football equipment rentals]

11:59.080 --> 12:00.030
A while ago, Qin Ao and the others

12:00.030 --> 12:02.360
also received some weird stuff like this.

12:07.270 --> 12:08.270
This...

12:10.720 --> 12:12.910
Could this be another puzzle
from the mysterious person?

12:12.910 --> 12:14.770
This is too much of a coincidence.

12:15.750 --> 12:16.610
Open it and see.

12:18.390 --> 12:19.210
[Destiny]

12:21.030 --> 12:22.150
Why is there a question on this?

12:22.150 --> 12:22.960
Destiny?

12:23.630 --> 12:25.260
[Question 1] [Question 2]

12:24.030 --> 12:25.550
Why are there questions in here?

12:25.390 --> 12:26.290
[Chance]

12:26.240 --> 12:28.600
Chance? These are also questions.

12:27.040 --> 12:28.110
[Question 1] [Question 2] [Question 3]

12:28.640 --> 12:29.640
[Map of Hongjing]

12:30.440 --> 12:31.360
A map?

12:31.150 --> 12:31.950
[Map of Hongjing]

12:34.510 --> 12:35.970
This string of numbers...

12:36.360 --> 12:37.440
What does it mean?

12:37.440 --> 12:38.570
Write it down first.

12:39.770 --> 12:41.240
[Question 1] [Question 2] [Question 3]

12:39.910 --> 12:41.550
I can't figure them out.

12:43.720 --> 12:44.750
What do you have?

12:45.320 --> 12:47.320
All questions we don't understand.

12:47.790 --> 12:49.720
We don't know what they are either.

12:51.440 --> 12:52.970
They're all math problems.

12:53.730 --> 12:55.630
So the fun puzzles you were talking about

12:55.630 --> 12:56.970
are just math problems?

12:57.240 --> 12:59.240
Last time it was a word puzzle.

12:59.240 --> 13:01.030
They were all four-character idioms.

13:01.030 --> 13:02.890
At least I could understand them.

13:03.260 --> 13:04.660
Among you,

13:04.790 --> 13:06.450
whose math grades are better?

13:12.550 --> 13:14.200
I think it's Yu Ming.

13:14.200 --> 13:16.060
Yeah, he can score over 80.

13:16.270 --> 13:17.120
Out of 100?

13:17.550 --> 13:18.390
Out of 150.

13:20.360 --> 13:21.800
I'll solve them then.

13:21.920 --> 13:23.980
You should be the one doing it anyway.

13:27.120 --> 13:28.480
After all, you're the genius

13:28.480 --> 13:30.170
who can score 140 out of 150.

13:30.560 --> 13:32.540
Show us what you've got, genius.

13:36.890 --> 13:40.830
[Determinant of Matrix A]

13:49.660 --> 13:49.880
[In the additive group of
residue classes modulo 4, Z4]

13:49.900 --> 13:50.230
[What is the order of the element 2?]

14:04.960 --> 14:06.120
The Destiny questions.

14:06.120 --> 14:08.440
For Question 4, 5, and 6,

14:10.030 --> 14:11.150
the answers I got

14:11.150 --> 14:16.000
are 6, 6, and 1 respectively.

14:19.670 --> 14:21.870
If we arrange the answers
for Chance and Fate questions

14:21.870 --> 14:23.080
separately...

14:24.260 --> 14:25.020
Look.

14:31.910 --> 14:34.110
I get dizzy just looking at numbers now.

14:35.320 --> 14:37.120
Then what's the connection
between these numbers?

14:37.120 --> 14:39.790
The connection between the numbers
might not be important.

14:39.790 --> 14:42.480
What's important
is their connection to the map.

14:40.220 --> 14:43.440
[Xu] [Qing] [Wen] [Wang]

14:42.480 --> 14:43.810
What's the connection?

14:45.030 --> 14:48.120
Why are the questions divided into
2 parts, "Destiny" and "Chance"?

14:48.120 --> 14:48.750
And why

14:49.500 --> 14:52.340
[Xu] [Qing] [Wen] [Wang]

14:49.790 --> 14:50.910
do both answers to Question 1

14:50.910 --> 14:52.670
contain decimal points?

14:56.670 --> 14:58.550
This is the map of Hongjing.

14:59.750 --> 15:01.270
If there are numbers anywhere...

15:01.270 --> 15:04.000
Exactly. They're coordinates—
latitude and longitude.

15:04.000 --> 15:05.390
The patterns in these numbers

15:05.390 --> 15:08.320
match the latitude and longitude
almost perfectly.

15:09.410 --> 15:12.570
29.58? 106.53?

15:09.980 --> 15:14.780
[Xu] [Qing] [Wen] [Wang]

15:12.600 --> 15:14.510
So the intersection point is...

15:15.340 --> 15:20.150
[Luoxin Photography Studio]

15:16.750 --> 15:18.010
A photography studio?

15:19.000 --> 15:20.910
Are we sure we're in the right place?

15:20.910 --> 15:21.640
Don't worry.

15:22.200 --> 15:23.840
Although math is my weak subject—

15:23.840 --> 15:25.630
I only got 141 out of 150
on the college entrance exam—

15:25.630 --> 15:27.290
I'm pretty sure I got it right.

15:28.510 --> 15:29.790
We haven't used the code

15:29.790 --> 15:31.080
on the back of this map yet.

15:31.080 --> 15:32.470
Could it be related to this place?

15:32.470 --> 15:33.480
Oh, right.

15:33.480 --> 15:35.790
Now that you mention it,
I suddenly remember.

15:35.790 --> 15:37.390
Photos from when we were kids

15:37.390 --> 15:39.150
do usually have codes written on the back.

15:39.150 --> 15:40.920
Fu, you're really smart.

15:41.270 --> 15:43.240
Let's go in and ask.

15:45.480 --> 15:47.080
-Come again.
-Thank you.

15:48.030 --> 15:48.550
Hello.

15:48.570 --> 15:49.150
Hello.

15:49.150 --> 15:50.480
Hi, excuse me.

15:50.480 --> 15:52.550
Is this photo code from your shop?

15:53.910 --> 15:54.600
In this day and age,

15:54.600 --> 15:56.200
we don't register photos
with codes anymore.

15:56.200 --> 15:57.320
Did you use them before?

15:57.320 --> 15:59.780
I think our former boss
used them in the past.

16:00.270 --> 16:00.790
Miss,

16:00.790 --> 16:03.030
could you please check for us?

16:03.030 --> 16:04.750
But I have urgent matters to handle
right now.

16:04.750 --> 16:05.550
I'm sorry.

16:05.550 --> 16:06.790
Maybe you could...

16:08.440 --> 16:09.040
Thank you.

16:10.910 --> 16:12.370
Let's step outside first.

16:14.910 --> 16:15.790
Excuse me.

16:21.560 --> 16:22.550
Thanks.

16:22.870 --> 16:23.320
It's nothing.

16:23.320 --> 16:24.270
Thank you, Miss.

16:25.360 --> 16:26.870
Could it be that we got the answer

16:26.870 --> 16:28.000
to the game wrong this time?

16:28.000 --> 16:28.960
It can't be.

16:28.960 --> 16:31.760
I think we just haven't found
the right answer yet.

16:34.490 --> 16:35.950
[A Snapshot of Time]

16:40.200 --> 16:41.860
A vintage photo-shoot event.

16:43.320 --> 16:45.180
What if we go in for a photo-shoot?

16:46.270 --> 16:49.310
Only couples and spouses can participate.

16:46.850 --> 16:47.690
[Event Rules: Open only to
couples and spouses]

16:47.710 --> 16:48.990
[Please make an appointment in advance.
Sessions will be arranged by appointment.]

16:49.550 --> 16:50.480
Who's going?

16:52.360 --> 16:53.480
Ms. Lin,

16:53.550 --> 16:55.390
The only person we have here
who might be able to take couple photos

16:55.390 --> 16:56.440
is you.

16:56.750 --> 16:59.000
Ms. Lin, you're the only one
who can do it.

16:59.000 --> 17:00.550
Ms. Lin, you're in your prime.

17:00.550 --> 17:01.960
You might as well
take some photos as a keepsake.

17:01.960 --> 17:03.030
It'll be a win-win.

17:03.030 --> 17:04.640
Think about it, Ms. Lin.

17:24.670 --> 17:28.030
[Little Savage Tribe]

17:25.349 --> 17:27.240
It took us an hour
to solve the math problems,

17:27.240 --> 17:29.350
but only 5 minutes to get kicked out.

17:30.400 --> 17:31.530
So what do we do next?

17:32.790 --> 17:33.360
Ms. Lin

17:33.400 --> 17:34.720
needs to find someone
to take couple photos with

17:34.720 --> 17:35.590
and sneak into the photo studio,

17:35.590 --> 17:37.270
so as to continue finding clues.

17:37.270 --> 17:38.680
How exciting!

17:38.680 --> 17:40.610
What kind of spy movie plot is this?

17:41.240 --> 17:42.400
Ms. Lin.

17:42.400 --> 17:44.920
So have you found someone
to take couple photos with?

17:44.920 --> 17:45.830
No.

17:46.270 --> 17:49.590
I was wondering if it's really necessary
to go this far.

17:49.590 --> 17:51.510
We don't even know
if the mysterious person

17:51.510 --> 17:53.830
who sent the gift box
is just messing with us.

17:53.830 --> 17:55.720
Don't you want to know the answer?

17:55.720 --> 17:57.290
I do.

17:57.750 --> 17:59.270
If it really comes down to it,

17:59.270 --> 18:01.070
I might as well just hire someone.

18:01.070 --> 18:02.830
It's only an act for the occasion anyway.

18:02.830 --> 18:04.200
Anyone will do.

18:05.000 --> 18:05.920
Ms. Lin.

18:05.920 --> 18:07.350
My uncle is very easygoing,

18:07.350 --> 18:08.350
and he has muscles.

18:08.350 --> 18:09.610
He's very photogenic.

18:13.110 --> 18:14.270
Ms. Lin.

18:14.270 --> 18:16.070
My cousin's also about the right age.

18:16.070 --> 18:17.650
How about I send you his pic?

18:17.880 --> 18:18.960
Handsome, right?

18:22.790 --> 18:23.920
My brother is also quite handsome.

18:23.920 --> 18:26.000
The guy upstairs from me could do.

18:26.000 --> 18:28.660
My cousin will definitely agree.
No need to ask.

18:42.880 --> 18:44.200
Coach, what's wrong?

18:44.680 --> 18:46.680
I saw the messages in the group chat.

18:47.110 --> 18:48.220
If it's Saturday,

18:48.400 --> 18:49.070
I have time.

18:51.070 --> 18:52.020
Are you saying

18:52.270 --> 18:54.800
you're willing to take couple photos
with me?

18:56.880 --> 18:57.960
As for the specific fee,

18:57.960 --> 19:00.560
let's settle it
based on the actual situation.

19:01.200 --> 19:02.880
Words cannot express my gratitude.

19:02.880 --> 19:03.610
Come with me.

19:07.110 --> 19:08.170
Where are we going?

19:08.480 --> 19:09.540
My grandpa's room.

19:14.960 --> 19:16.620
Are we looking for something?

19:16.890 --> 19:19.270
The clothes my grandpa and grandma
left behind.

19:19.270 --> 19:21.640
That's a vintage photography studio,
you know.

19:21.640 --> 19:23.000
I want to wear their clothes

19:23.000 --> 19:24.800
to make it feel more ceremonial.

19:25.030 --> 19:28.430
-Actually, I have...
-You look over there. I'll search this.

19:38.030 --> 19:39.750
I haven't found anything yet.

19:40.200 --> 19:41.310
What about you?

19:41.310 --> 19:42.440
Here...

20:01.830 --> 20:03.040
This amusement park

20:03.270 --> 20:05.310
was the source of my childhood joy.

20:06.000 --> 20:08.240
Grandpa used to take me there
all the time.

20:08.240 --> 20:09.960
Grandpa and I even used to make bets

20:09.960 --> 20:12.790
on who would get on the carousel first.

20:21.640 --> 20:22.370
What's this?

20:25.200 --> 20:26.600
Can you wiggle your ears?

20:26.830 --> 20:27.640
Like this.

20:36.920 --> 20:38.050
Impressive, right?

20:39.750 --> 20:40.480
Impressive.

20:40.790 --> 20:41.480
You try it.

20:45.160 --> 20:46.090
Did they wiggle?

20:54.350 --> 20:55.720
Formal name Lin Wanxing,

20:55.720 --> 20:59.590
nickname Shining Star Genius...

20:59.590 --> 21:00.590
Princess.

21:03.550 --> 21:04.810
You're laughing at me.

21:07.030 --> 21:07.680
I'm not laughing.

21:07.680 --> 21:10.210
I could even see your teeth.
Still denying it.

21:10.400 --> 21:11.750
You're still laughing.

21:11.750 --> 21:15.110
I'm not laughing at you,
Shining Star Genius Princess.

21:15.110 --> 21:16.240
Let's keep looking.

21:28.400 --> 21:29.440
Found it.

21:34.550 --> 21:36.270
Isn't this too small for me?

21:36.880 --> 21:38.070
My grandfather was also very tall.

21:38.070 --> 21:39.240
You can definitely fit into it.

21:39.240 --> 21:40.370
Just make do with it.

21:53.030 --> 21:53.830
Felix Yu,

21:53.770 --> 21:56.880
[Felix Yu]

21:53.830 --> 21:55.480
I have an honorable task for you:

21:55.480 --> 21:58.140
go to my house and sneak out
a vintage suit for me.

21:59.240 --> 22:01.200
Which house? In Hengjiu?

22:02.660 --> 22:03.230
Yes.

22:04.070 --> 22:06.240
What's going on? Cosplay?

22:06.240 --> 22:08.300
I think I found my grandmother's too.

22:08.440 --> 22:09.640
It should be this one.

22:12.310 --> 22:13.590
They seem to be a set.

22:25.300 --> 22:28.200
[Felix Yu]

22:25.880 --> 22:26.440
Hello, hello, hello?

22:26.440 --> 22:27.240
Where are you?

22:27.440 --> 22:28.030
I don't need your help anymore.

22:28.030 --> 22:29.000
You may leave.

23:03.790 --> 23:04.880
Ms. Lin.

23:22.960 --> 23:23.830
How do I look?

23:26.110 --> 23:28.110
A bit less handsome than my grandpa.

23:32.960 --> 23:34.690
Might as well commit to the act.

23:54.710 --> 23:56.320
[A Snapshot of Time]

23:56.590 --> 23:57.350
Hello, Boss.

23:57.350 --> 23:58.750
We have a 1:30 appointment

23:58.750 --> 23:59.840
for a couples' photo-shoot session.

23:59.840 --> 24:00.550
Hello.

24:01.160 --> 24:01.680
Okay.

24:01.680 --> 24:02.750
Let me check.

24:04.160 --> 24:06.000
Mr. Wang and Ms. Lin, right?

24:06.000 --> 24:06.400
Yes.

24:06.790 --> 24:08.720
Here are some styles for your reference.

24:08.720 --> 24:09.680
You two can take a look first.

24:09.680 --> 24:11.410
-Thank you.
-I'll go get ready.

24:28.510 --> 24:29.700
No match.

24:31.350 --> 24:32.810
Let's go check over there.

24:45.070 --> 24:46.600
There are some more up here.

24:47.720 --> 24:49.440
Boss, we'll wait for you upstairs.

24:49.440 --> 24:50.440
Help yourselves.

25:06.660 --> 25:10.060
[Golden Wedding Anniversary]

25:24.640 --> 25:27.410
[August 23, 2021]

25:28.590 --> 25:29.400
What's wrong?

25:31.400 --> 25:32.200
Found it.

25:33.880 --> 25:35.340
They're my grandparents.

25:38.920 --> 25:40.160
Sorry

25:40.160 --> 25:41.240
to keep you waiting.

25:41.240 --> 25:42.750
We're all set for the photo-shoot.

25:42.750 --> 25:43.510
Let me just adjust the lights.

25:43.510 --> 25:44.200
Boss.

25:44.830 --> 25:46.310
Excuse me, but

25:46.310 --> 25:48.010
did you take this photo?

25:48.270 --> 25:49.240
I didn't take this.

25:49.240 --> 25:50.270
My dad took it.

25:50.640 --> 25:52.270
This is his proudest work.

25:52.270 --> 25:54.160
And he shot it with old-fashioned film.

25:54.160 --> 25:56.020
See, he even numbered this photo.

25:57.350 --> 25:59.480
Can you please sell it to me?

26:00.500 --> 26:02.170
No can do. I'm sorry.

26:02.310 --> 26:03.550
Please, Boss.

26:03.550 --> 26:06.100
They were my closest family in this world.

26:06.270 --> 26:07.630
And they are long gone.

26:07.960 --> 26:10.200
I really want to buy it as a keepsake.

26:10.200 --> 26:11.660
Please make an exception.

26:12.440 --> 26:13.440
I'm sorry.

26:14.000 --> 26:16.330
Let's just proceed with the photo-shoot.

26:21.100 --> 26:21.440
[Golden Wedding Anniversary]

26:24.350 --> 26:26.150
Are you guys Xunya and Yuanyuan?

26:26.680 --> 26:28.550
You're here to pick up your photos, right?

26:28.550 --> 26:29.000
Dad.

26:29.000 --> 26:30.600
Why did you come downstairs?

26:30.880 --> 26:31.790
This is my dad.

26:31.790 --> 26:32.720
He's a bit...

26:32.720 --> 26:34.580
He thinks it's still 30 years ago.

26:34.890 --> 26:37.010
I've been waiting for you.

26:37.110 --> 26:38.680
You're finally here.

26:38.680 --> 26:41.350
I want to take another picture of you.

26:41.350 --> 26:43.000
Get ready, you two.

26:43.000 --> 26:44.350
Come on, get ready.

26:44.350 --> 26:45.920
It seems this old gentleman

26:45.920 --> 26:48.880
-is a friend of my grandparents.
-Do you mind letting my dad take the photos?

26:48.880 --> 26:49.540
No problem.

26:49.960 --> 26:50.960
T-Thank you.

26:50.960 --> 26:52.170
I'll go get ready.

26:52.790 --> 26:55.440
Could he be the one who led us here?

26:55.640 --> 26:56.590
Are you alright?

26:59.050 --> 27:00.660
I'll play along for now.

27:07.000 --> 27:08.650
Oh no, it's blurry.

27:09.110 --> 27:10.040
Let's try again.

27:10.880 --> 27:12.720
Come on, get ready.

27:12.720 --> 27:14.750
One, two...

27:16.830 --> 27:17.480
What's going on?

27:17.480 --> 27:18.720
It's still blurry.

27:19.970 --> 27:21.210
I'm sorry, you two.

27:21.240 --> 27:22.640
Sorry for wasting your time.

27:22.640 --> 27:24.370
It's fine. We're not in a hurry.

27:24.440 --> 27:25.370
Let's try again.

27:26.110 --> 27:27.160
How about I do it, Dad?

27:27.160 --> 27:27.620
Go away.

27:29.270 --> 27:30.470
Use the tripod. Here.

27:34.400 --> 27:35.160
Xunya.

27:35.830 --> 27:37.750
Did you two have a fight?

27:39.110 --> 27:40.070
-We didn't.
-We didn't.

27:40.070 --> 27:42.640
Then show me some chemistry.

27:43.200 --> 27:43.920
Chemistry?

27:44.640 --> 27:45.590
Chemistry.

27:47.960 --> 27:49.270
He probably means

27:48.350 --> 27:50.420
♪ I caught your eyes ♪

27:50.350 --> 27:51.830
a little physical contact

27:50.890 --> 27:53.260
♪ On the summer night ♪

27:51.830 --> 27:53.510
and a brighter smile.

27:53.750 --> 27:59.260
♪ A star that glows so bright ♪

27:56.880 --> 27:57.830
This is good.

27:58.480 --> 27:59.510
Come on.

27:59.830 --> 28:01.680
Much better. Let's take another one.

28:00.780 --> 28:03.040
♪ A spark in my heart ♪

28:02.110 --> 28:03.110
Be closer.

28:03.740 --> 28:09.530
♪ Disappear in my dream, secretly ♪

28:07.790 --> 28:09.850
Ms. Lin, put your hand on my shoulder.

28:12.920 --> 28:18.340
♪ With the evening breeze
whispering in my ear ♪

28:16.880 --> 28:17.640
Look at me.

28:19.070 --> 28:24.870
♪ Fireworks bloom across the sky ♪

28:25.290 --> 28:27.980
♪ Shimmering in your eyes ♪

28:28.250 --> 28:34.620
♪ And spreading into
a gentle sea of stars ♪

28:37.320 --> 28:39.390
♪ Every night ♪

28:38.550 --> 28:39.160
Good.

28:39.750 --> 28:40.790
This one is good.

28:40.070 --> 28:42.320
♪ I reach for starlight ♪

28:42.940 --> 28:44.970
♪ Wandering through dreams with you ♪

28:45.340 --> 28:48.030
♪ I follow the beat of my heart ♪

28:48.880 --> 28:51.480
♪ Like dust floating in the air ♪

28:52.320 --> 28:54.230
♪ Because of your love ♪

28:55.010 --> 28:59.790
♪ I shine brilliantly ♪

28:57.830 --> 29:00.960
Isn't the size a bit too big?

29:00.960 --> 29:01.960
It's well taken.

29:04.200 --> 29:06.730
We absolutely cannot let
those kids see this.

29:07.510 --> 29:09.000
Are the photos ready?

29:17.110 --> 29:19.240
This bracelet is...

29:24.750 --> 29:25.720
You are...

29:28.400 --> 29:30.640
Y-You're not Yuanyuan.

29:31.350 --> 29:32.200
Who are you?

29:33.510 --> 29:35.110
Yuanyuan was my grandmother.

29:35.110 --> 29:36.370
My name is Lin Wanxing.

29:36.680 --> 29:39.610
I'm the granddaughter of
Lin Xunya and Shen Shuyuan.

29:43.200 --> 29:44.000
Right.

29:45.550 --> 29:46.850
I just remembered

29:47.270 --> 29:49.790
something very important.

29:50.590 --> 29:57.560
[9 months ago]

30:05.750 --> 30:08.070
Hello. Hello?

30:09.200 --> 30:10.160
Excuse me,

30:10.160 --> 30:11.680
are you the owner of this shop?

30:11.680 --> 30:12.550
Are you here for a photo-shoot?

30:12.550 --> 30:14.080
I'm here to collect a photo.

30:17.240 --> 30:17.960
Come on in.

30:19.070 --> 30:20.240
Lin Xunya.

30:22.550 --> 30:23.510
Who are you?

30:23.830 --> 30:26.110
Why didn't Xunya come
pick it up himself?

30:24.850 --> 30:26.490
[Receipt]

30:27.200 --> 30:29.590
Shortly after this photo was taken,

30:29.830 --> 30:31.760
Mr. Lin was diagnosed with cancer.

30:32.350 --> 30:33.880
He passed away not long ago.

30:37.350 --> 30:40.240
What about his wife, Shen Shuyuan?

30:41.070 --> 30:43.200
Mrs. Shen also passed away

30:44.110 --> 30:45.570
not long after Mr. Lin did.

30:49.310 --> 30:50.440
I see.

30:53.810 --> 30:56.780
[Lin Xunya and Shen Shuyuan's
Golden Wedding Anniversary]

30:54.830 --> 30:56.480
I really like this photo,

30:57.310 --> 30:58.480
so I enlarged it

30:59.240 --> 31:00.900
and kept it hanging upstairs.

31:01.480 --> 31:03.640
I was planning
to take another photo for them

31:03.640 --> 31:05.500
when they came to pick this one up.

31:06.030 --> 31:07.490
Who would have thought...

31:11.350 --> 31:12.240
At least

31:14.160 --> 31:15.760
they're together again now.

31:17.350 --> 31:18.150
Oh, by the way.

31:20.160 --> 31:21.830
I have one more small request.

31:22.510 --> 31:24.030
I hope you can do me this favor.

31:24.030 --> 31:25.480
Since you know Xunya,

31:25.480 --> 31:27.610
that makes you sort of a friend of mine.

31:27.680 --> 31:28.350
Go ahead.

31:33.200 --> 31:34.460
Open it and take a look.

31:42.640 --> 31:43.790
I also have no idea

31:43.790 --> 31:45.790
why he entrusted these things to me.

31:46.160 --> 31:47.240
He said

31:47.240 --> 31:49.810
that one day, Xunya's descendants

31:50.070 --> 31:51.200
would come to collect them.

31:51.200 --> 31:53.790
So I just accepted them in a daze.

31:53.960 --> 31:54.720
Sir,

31:54.720 --> 31:56.960
do you remember his name?

31:58.880 --> 32:00.550
I don't think he left a name.

32:04.220 --> 32:10.250
[No. 7, Wutong Road]

32:36.640 --> 32:41.880
♪ Waiting for a dark cloud
to pass by you ♪

32:42.760 --> 32:47.340
♪ Listen closely to its cries ♪

32:49.130 --> 32:54.130
♪ The heavy rain will wash away
your reflection ♪

32:55.030 --> 33:00.630
♪ And carry it toward distant scenery ♪

32:58.790 --> 33:02.980
[No. 7, Wutong Road]

33:02.040 --> 33:07.700
♪ Every experience has its meaning ♪

33:04.400 --> 33:05.240
Give it to me.

33:08.650 --> 33:13.420
♪ Scene by scene, they come together
to form who I am ♪

33:15.080 --> 33:20.460
♪ Even the wounds
that leave behind their marks ♪

33:21.380 --> 33:26.220
♪ Have taught me how to heal myself ♪

33:27.400 --> 33:33.060
♪ The love I have given,
the love I have received ♪

33:28.350 --> 33:29.590
Grandpa!

33:30.790 --> 33:32.350
What brings you here, Wanxing?

33:32.350 --> 33:33.920
I have something to tell you.

33:33.920 --> 33:35.070
I saw a really big tadpole

33:34.010 --> 33:39.490
♪ Every one of them gives me the strength
not to fear being hurt ♪

33:35.070 --> 33:37.320
at school,

33:37.340 --> 33:39.590
and I want to bring it home
and raise it into a frog.

33:39.590 --> 33:41.310
Okay. Go find Grandma.

33:40.450 --> 33:46.060
♪ Let my tears be carried away,
back into the ocean ♪

33:41.310 --> 33:42.350
I'm in the middle of a class.

33:42.350 --> 33:42.960
Be good.

33:42.960 --> 33:43.640
Let's go to the yard.

33:43.640 --> 33:45.160
Alright, where were we?

33:45.160 --> 33:46.420
Here, "hold the line."

33:46.590 --> 33:48.520
-And this.
-Don't make a sound.

33:46.920 --> 33:52.080
♪ And blown toward flowers
blooming far away ♪

33:48.960 --> 33:50.360
Let's go draw over there.

33:50.510 --> 33:51.510
Come on.

33:51.510 --> 33:54.030
Here, give me the bag.

33:53.470 --> 33:58.800
♪ I fill the blank spaces of life
with colors ♪

33:54.920 --> 33:56.200
Come on, sit here.

33:56.200 --> 33:57.240
Okay, Grandma.

33:57.240 --> 33:58.640
Grandma, time to draw.

33:59.240 --> 34:00.790
What do you want to draw?

33:59.540 --> 34:05.020
♪ My dreams are not afraid to awaken;
they continue to exist ♪

34:06.050 --> 34:11.520
♪ I go beyond the dark clouds
and feel the haze disperse ♪

34:12.699 --> 34:18.400
♪ Let me understand myself more clearly ♪

34:20.110 --> 34:21.409
Bye.

34:22.219 --> 34:23.800
Goodbye. Goodbye.

34:24.280 --> 34:25.000
Grandpa!

34:25.480 --> 34:26.510
Look what I drew.

34:27.070 --> 34:28.760
You drew so well.

34:28.760 --> 34:30.510
What is it that you drew?

34:30.710 --> 34:32.030
This is Grandpa,

34:32.030 --> 34:33.030
this is me,

34:33.030 --> 34:34.320
and this is Grandma.

34:36.510 --> 34:38.960
You drew so well.

34:36.620 --> 34:41.670
♪ Every experience has its meaning ♪

34:38.960 --> 34:41.360
You won't be able to draw this
when you grow up.

34:41.360 --> 34:43.550
Grandpa, your watch is so pretty.

34:42.889 --> 34:47.420
♪ Scene by scene, they come together
to form who I am ♪

34:43.550 --> 34:44.880
I want it too.

34:44.880 --> 34:46.920
This was a gift

34:46.920 --> 34:48.150
from Grandma.

34:49.320 --> 34:54.300
♪ Even the wounds
that leave behind their marks ♪

34:49.360 --> 34:51.480
This was given to me by your Grandma

34:51.480 --> 34:53.230
on my first day as a teacher.

34:53.230 --> 34:54.760
How can I just give it to you?

34:54.960 --> 34:56.230
Grandma's being unfair.

34:55.480 --> 35:01.890
♪ Have taught me how to heal myself ♪

34:58.070 --> 34:59.510
You're still too young.

34:59.510 --> 35:01.230
How about I buy you

35:01.230 --> 35:02.630
a cartoon watch first, okay?

35:02.630 --> 35:04.440
I want Grandpa's.

35:04.490 --> 35:09.970
♪ I fill the blank spaces of life
with colors ♪

35:05.000 --> 35:06.480
Alright, alright.

35:06.480 --> 35:09.630
Once I retire from
Yuanyuan Tutoring Center,

35:09.630 --> 35:10.960
I'll give you this watch.

35:10.960 --> 35:11.920
Pinky swear.

35:11.070 --> 35:16.330
♪ My dreams are not afraid to awaken;
they continue to exist ♪

35:12.190 --> 35:12.670
Okay.

35:13.480 --> 35:14.320
Pinky swear.

35:14.320 --> 35:16.000
What does Yuanyuan mean?

35:14.540 --> 35:17.180
[Yuanyuan Tutoring Center]

35:16.370 --> 35:17.370
Yuanyuan.

35:17.400 --> 35:19.710
Yuanyuan is Grandma's nickname.

35:17.850 --> 35:23.020
♪ I go beyond the dark clouds
and feel the haze disperse ♪

35:19.710 --> 35:20.550
Her parents gave her this nickname

35:20.550 --> 35:23.230
with a special meaning.

35:23.230 --> 35:26.000
"Yuanyuan" was meant to remind her
to study diligently.

35:24.070 --> 35:29.490
♪ Let me understand myself more clearly ♪

35:26.000 --> 35:28.510
“Yuanyuan" comes from
"the countless living beings."

35:28.210 --> 35:30.120
[Yuanyuan Tutoring Center]

35:28.510 --> 35:31.110
The purpose of studying is to care for

35:31.110 --> 35:32.510
and serve all living beings.

35:31.110 --> 35:35.690
♪ Take away my reflection ♪

35:34.230 --> 35:35.800
Yuanyuan Tutoring Center?

35:36.960 --> 35:37.840
Yuanyuan

35:37.530 --> 35:44.760
♪ And go in search of distant scenery ♪

35:38.920 --> 35:40.400
was my grandma's name.

36:00.670 --> 36:02.530
My grandpa was a Chinese teacher,

36:02.920 --> 36:04.780
and my grandma was an art teacher.

36:09.800 --> 36:11.710
They taught for a lifetime,

36:13.440 --> 36:15.710
and didn't stop after retiring.

36:50.710 --> 36:52.910
This watch used to belong to my grandpa.

36:58.320 --> 36:59.280
He promised

37:02.360 --> 37:03.630
that once I grew up,

37:05.360 --> 37:06.960
he'd give it to me.

37:36.000 --> 37:38.260
Your grandpa took really good care of it.

37:38.840 --> 37:40.400
It looks brand new.

37:50.030 --> 37:53.190
Once I retire from
Yuanyuan Tutoring Center,

37:53.190 --> 37:54.480
I'll give this watch to you.

37:54.480 --> 37:55.400
Pinky swear.

37:55.710 --> 37:56.190
Okay.

38:13.340 --> 38:17.790
[Yuanyuan Tutoring Center]

38:20.360 --> 38:22.960
“Yuanyuan" comes from
"the countless living beings."

38:22.960 --> 38:24.110
The purpose of studying

38:24.110 --> 38:27.190
is to care for and serve
all living beings.

38:34.480 --> 38:35.610
I've made up my mind.

38:36.110 --> 38:37.190
I will stay here

38:37.800 --> 38:39.190
and tutor those kids.

38:39.920 --> 38:41.180
For all living beings,

38:41.630 --> 38:43.160
for the fruits of hard work—

38:44.360 --> 38:46.320
what Grandpa and Grandma
devoted their lives to doing,

38:46.320 --> 38:47.960
I'll carry it on for them.

39:17.640 --> 39:18.570
Grandpa.

39:19.760 --> 39:21.360
I think I finally understand

39:22.800 --> 39:25.440
why you sent me to
Hongjing No. 8 High School.

39:28.400 --> 39:29.280
Don't worry.

39:30.110 --> 39:31.060
From now on,

39:32.470 --> 39:35.400
I'll never give up on myself again
because of anyone.

39:44.320 --> 39:45.780
Over this past month or so,

39:47.360 --> 39:49.030
I've been really happy.

39:51.550 --> 39:54.110
Thank you for your gift, Grandpa.

39:59.840 --> 40:00.590
Grandpa,

40:02.320 --> 40:03.190
Grandma,

40:06.030 --> 40:07.880
I miss you so much.

40:12.230 --> 40:14.850
Although I don't know
who the mysterious person is

40:14.850 --> 40:18.100
or where he wants to lead us,

40:18.360 --> 40:21.120
I can feel his kindness and help.

40:21.320 --> 40:23.110
Maybe if we let nature take its course,

40:23.110 --> 40:25.320
we'll eventually find out
who he really is someday.

40:25.320 --> 40:26.030
Which number was it again?

40:26.030 --> 40:27.300
-No. 7, I think.
-No. 7.

40:27.320 --> 40:29.000
-Where is No. 7?
-No. 7.

40:29.000 --> 40:30.670
-This is No. 6.
-That one.

40:30.670 --> 40:31.960
-This is No. 7.
-This is No. 5.

40:31.960 --> 40:33.030
Here it is. Over here.

40:33.030 --> 40:34.320
No. 7 is here.

40:34.320 --> 40:35.150
It's so big.

40:35.150 --> 40:37.400
-Do you think it's Ms. Lin's house?
-This is No. 7?

40:37.400 --> 40:37.920
That's very likely.

40:37.920 --> 40:38.850
Such a big house.

40:39.630 --> 40:40.880
Why is it so run-down inside?

40:40.880 --> 40:41.590
It's too heavy. Put it down for now.

40:41.590 --> 40:43.070
-It's run-down.
-Hello? Anyone in there?

40:43.070 --> 40:44.480
-There's no one.
-Anyone in there?

40:44.480 --> 40:45.480
H-How could this be?

40:45.480 --> 40:46.740
There are people here.

40:47.190 --> 40:48.620
-Ms. Lin.
-Ms. Lin.

40:48.640 --> 40:49.360
Coach.

40:49.360 --> 40:50.760
It was Coach who asked us to come.

40:50.760 --> 40:52.550
Ms. Lin, why are you here too?

40:53.070 --> 40:53.960
Because this is the place where

40:53.960 --> 40:56.480
you'll be having your tutoring sessions.

40:56.480 --> 40:58.500
It's also our team's secret base.

40:59.230 --> 41:00.150
Secret base?

41:00.150 --> 41:02.230
This whole building?
We have such a big place to ourselves?

41:02.230 --> 41:03.000
You see this?

41:03.000 --> 41:04.630
This is pretty cool.

41:09.920 --> 41:11.400
It's this clean?

41:11.400 --> 41:12.830
This is the room.

41:14.460 --> 41:15.460
It's a classroom.

41:17.800 --> 41:19.150
Even the door's broken.

41:21.440 --> 41:23.510
Yuanyuan Tutoring Center?

41:24.030 --> 41:24.840
So

41:24.840 --> 41:27.770
our secret base is called
Yuanyuan Tutoring Center.

41:28.710 --> 41:30.840
How much longer do you think
it'll take us to finish cleaning today?

41:30.840 --> 41:32.920
At least 3 or 4 hours.

41:32.920 --> 41:34.670
Boss, are you wearing a watch?

41:34.670 --> 41:36.190
Zheng is. What time is it?

41:36.190 --> 41:37.880
Yeah, check what time it is.

41:39.960 --> 41:41.150
Clean it properly.

41:41.360 --> 41:42.400
Just do your own work.

41:42.400 --> 41:43.550
You talk too much.

41:47.400 --> 41:48.480
There are so many people here.

41:48.480 --> 41:50.000
-Fu, you're here.
-Yes.

41:50.000 --> 41:51.230
Come on, Fu.

41:51.230 --> 41:52.230
Mop the outside first.

41:52.230 --> 41:52.880
I'll help you first,

41:52.880 --> 41:53.810
then you help me.

41:57.670 --> 41:58.800
You guys be careful.

41:59.150 --> 42:00.400
Ms. Lin.

42:03.550 --> 42:04.920
If I'm not mistaken,

42:04.920 --> 42:06.190
you've been wiping this marble counter

42:06.190 --> 42:07.710
for 20 minutes.

42:07.710 --> 42:10.460
I said we'd come clean this morning,

42:10.630 --> 42:13.440
but I never meant this early.

42:13.440 --> 42:15.000
I'm out of energy.

42:15.880 --> 42:17.550
About to crash.

42:18.030 --> 42:20.030
An hour in the morning
is worth two in the evening.

42:20.030 --> 42:23.670
An hour in the morning is something
I simply can't afford.

42:24.670 --> 42:25.630
You can still joke around.

42:25.630 --> 42:27.710
It seems you're not really out of energy.

42:27.710 --> 42:29.170
I've got a mission for you.

42:30.800 --> 42:32.460
See that recliner over there?

42:32.840 --> 42:33.880
I just cleaned it.

42:33.880 --> 42:35.150
Go lie down there.

42:35.150 --> 42:37.510
Whenever a mop comes by,
lift your legs up.

42:37.760 --> 42:39.090
Think you can handle it?

42:39.920 --> 42:41.150
Thank you.

42:42.110 --> 42:43.760
-Mop.
-Where's the mop?

42:43.760 --> 42:44.550
Right here.

42:58.110 --> 42:59.150
Why is it so dirty?

42:59.150 --> 43:00.280
Why is it so big?

43:00.280 --> 43:01.650
It's too big, bro.

43:04.230 --> 43:05.190
There's a balcony here.

43:05.190 --> 43:07.190
How long will it take for us to clean?

43:07.230 --> 43:08.150
Guys!

43:08.150 --> 43:10.070
There's another huge balcony up here!

43:10.070 --> 43:11.870
-Let's go take a look.
-Let's go.

43:18.360 --> 43:20.010
The view is so nice.

43:20.320 --> 43:22.360
We'll be having classes here from now on.

43:22.360 --> 43:22.920
Yeah.

43:22.920 --> 43:24.670
-This feels so great.
-We'll be having classes here.

43:24.670 --> 43:26.480
Let's start sweeping from the bottom
and work our way up.

43:26.480 --> 43:27.840
-Sure.
-Let's go.

43:48.790 --> 43:51.170
♪ Night slips through my fingers ♪

43:52.020 --> 43:55.860
♪ Embracing the coldness of wakefulness ♪

43:56.730 --> 43:58.560
♪ Whispering my thoughts alone ♪

43:59.090 --> 44:03.990
♪ Saying goodbye to the evening breeze
we met by chance ♪

44:04.580 --> 44:07.230
♪ Staying with the jasmine blossoms
until late spring ♪

44:07.900 --> 44:10.990
♪ Watching their elegance fade,
their fragrance disappear ♪

44:12.290 --> 44:15.310
♪ I once dreamed of beauty ♪

44:16.230 --> 44:20.090
♪ And I accept that
regrets may grow wild ♪

44:20.770 --> 44:22.970
♪ Look, beneath the sunlight ♪

44:23.760 --> 44:27.680
♪ In the dancing specks of dust ♪

44:28.480 --> 44:31.240
♪ I'm grateful I never lost my sincerity ♪

44:31.900 --> 44:35.670
♪ Or my gift for happiness ♪

44:37.240 --> 44:39.310
♪ Sharing my warmth with a passing rain ♪

44:40.050 --> 44:43.670
♪ Quietly feeling its journey ♪

44:45.100 --> 44:47.060
♪ Like a firefly vanishing in an instant ♪

44:48.010 --> 44:51.870
♪ Still beautiful in its entirety ♪

44:52.580 --> 44:55.030
♪ There's no need to seek a final answer ♪

44:56.130 --> 44:59.900
♪ Let the ending remain with
questions unanswered ♪

45:00.700 --> 45:03.130
♪ No need to prove it with promises ♪

45:04.250 --> 45:07.760
♪ The dusk when we once vowed
to stay together ♪

45:09.240 --> 45:11.210
♪ No need to cling to forever ♪

45:11.850 --> 45:12.380
♪ Allow separation to happen ♪
